          "name": "What makes a good employer branding video?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Honesty. Real employees, real workplaces and a clear picture of who thrives at your company. A good film makes the right candidates think 'that could be me' — and lets the wrong ones self-select out before they apply. Generic promises and stock footage do the opposite."
