          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How long does an employer branding video take to produce?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "You see a first draft within about two weeks of the shoot. We agree on the full timeline before we start — and we stick to it. Everything runs in-house, from concept to final cut, which keeps the schedule tight."
          }
        },
